    <detaileddescription>
<para>This <ref refid="classFuncRate" kindref="compound">FuncRate</ref> manages a one-way reaction whose rate is determined by a <ref refid="classFunction" kindref="compound">Function</ref>. It has no substrates, just controls the rate of change of a target molecule.</para>
<para>dtarget/dt = func( x0, x1, x2..., t )</para>
<para>The values x0, x1, x2.. are numbers at this point. So is the rate output of this function. There may be a problem if there is a volume change. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
